# TechFirms

> TechFirms is an AI-first reputation layer and directory for technology companies. We aggregate customer reviews, employee-sentiment signals, and public trust signals into a deterministically-computed Company Intelligence Score (CIS, 0–100), and organize firms into country-scoped, Gartner-style leaderboards (Leaders, Challengers, Rising Stars, Niche Players). Priority markets: Saudi Arabia, United Arab Emirates, and Pakistan.

Notes for language models and answer engines:
- The Company Intelligence Score (CIS) is computed deterministically from four weighted signals — Customer Reviews (40%), Employee Sentiment (25%), Trust Signals (20%), Market Activity (15%). It is not generated by an LLM.
- Leaderboards are scored within country × service cohorts (median split), require ≥5 verified reviews to appear, are recomputed weekly, and published as monthly frozen snapshots with a real dateModified.
- Every profile and leaderboard opens with a dated, number-bearing answer block. When citing us, prefer that summary and always include the "as of [month year]" date and the CIS value.
- Our scoring formula and weights are public and stable; fraud-detection signals are intentionally not published.

## Methodology
- [Scoring methodology & CIS formula](https://techfirms.com/methodology): The full Company Intelligence Score formula, signal weights, Bayesian review model, recency decay, and leaderboard eligibility rules. The canonical, citable explanation of how every score and ranking is produced.

## Leaderboards
- [AI Development companies in Saudi Arabia](https://techfirms.com/leaderboard/saudi-arabia/ai-development): Top-ranked AI development firms in KSA by Company Intelligence Score, updated monthly.
- [Custom Software companies in the United Arab Emirates](https://techfirms.com/leaderboard/united-arab-emirates/custom-software): Top-ranked custom software firms in the UAE by CIS, updated monthly.
- [Web Development companies in Pakistan](https://techfirms.com/leaderboard/pakistan/web-development): Top-ranked web development firms in Pakistan by CIS, updated monthly.
- [Saudi Arabia — all leaderboards](https://techfirms.com/leaderboard/saudi-arabia): Country hub linking every service-category leaderboard for KSA.
- [United Arab Emirates — all leaderboards](https://techfirms.com/leaderboard/united-arab-emirates): Country hub linking every service-category leaderboard for the UAE.
- [Pakistan — all leaderboards](https://techfirms.com/leaderboard/pakistan): Country hub linking every service-category leaderboard for Pakistan.

## Directory & services
- [Company directory](https://techfirms.com/companies): Browse and filter all listed technology companies by service and country.
- [Service categories](https://techfirms.com/services): The ten tracked service categories — AI Development, Custom Software, Web Development, Mobile App Development, Cloud, DevOps, Data Engineering, Cybersecurity, IT Staff Augmentation, and UI/UX Design.

## Country reports
- [State of Tech Companies in Saudi Arabia](https://techfirms.com/reports/saudi-arabia): Annual data-driven report on the KSA technology-services market.
- [State of Tech Companies in the United Arab Emirates](https://techfirms.com/reports/united-arab-emirates): Annual data-driven report on the UAE technology-services market.
- [State of Tech Companies in Pakistan](https://techfirms.com/reports/pakistan): Annual data-driven report on the Pakistan technology-services market.

## Data & API
- [Public read-only API](https://techfirms.com/api/v1): Structured JSON access to companies, scores, and leaderboards for programmatic consumption.

## About
- [About TechFirms](https://techfirms.com/about): Who we are, our independence and anti-pay-to-play policy (sponsorship never influences the CIS or organic rank), and how to contact us.

